# Project Overview

## Purpose
Establish a modern, maintainable baseline for full-stack projects using Next.js (TypeScript) for frontend and FastAPI (Python) for backend.

## Default Stacks
- **Frontend:** Next.js (TypeScript), Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui
- **Backend:** FastAPI (Python)

## Testing
- **Backend:** Pytest
- **Frontend:** Jest, React Testing Library

## CI
- GitHub Actions for lint, test, build

## Coding Conventions
- Functional JavaScript/TypeScript
- Conventional Commits
- Minimal, example-driven unit tests
